DEFINITION:
____________________________________________________________________
Main news container: $main
	- div.main-content div#infinity-cont
Main news article:  $article
    - $main div.items > article
Main news article link:
	- $article[] a.article-link { href }
Main news article title:
    - $article[] h2.article-title { text }
Main news article desc:
	- $article[] section.article-intro { text }
Main news article date:
    - $article[] dd.published { text }

PAYLOAD:
____________________________________________________________________
function ca_payload() {
var ca_tools = {
	encode : function b64EncodeUnicode(str) {
		return btoa(encodeURIComponent(str).replace(/%([0-9A-F]{2})/g, function(match, p1) {
			return String.fromCharCode('0x' + p1);
		}));
	},
	decode : function b64DecodeUnicode(str) {
		return decodeURIComponent(Array.prototype.map.call(atob(str), function(c) {
			return '%' + ('00' + c.charCodeAt(0).toString(16)).slice(-2);
		}).join(''));
	},
	tojson : function(obj) { return JSON.stringify(obj); },
	toobj  : function(obj) { return JSON.parse(obj); }
};
var ca_result = { status: 0, mes: 'done', count: 0, obj: [] };
var ca_art = jQuery('div.main-content div#infinity-cont div.items article');
if (ca_art.length) {
	ca_result.count = ca_art.length;
	ca_art.each(function(i,e){
		var $e = jQuery(e);
		var add = {
			link  : $e.find('a.article-link')[0].href || "",
			img	  : $e.find('a.article-link > img')[0].src || "",
			title : $e.find('h2.article-title').text() || "",
			desc  : $e.find('section.article-intro').text() || "",
			date  : $e.find('dd.published').text() || "",
		};
		add.title = add.title.replace(/(\r\n|\n|\r|\t|  )/gm,"");
		add.desc = add.desc.replace(/(\r\n|\n|\r|\t|  )/gm,"");
		add.date = add.date.replace(/(\r\n|\n|\r|\t|  )/gm,"");
		ca_result.obj.push(add);
	});
} else { ca_result.status = 1; ca_result.mes = "cant get articels"; }
return ca_tools.encode(ca_tools.tojson(ca_result));
}
ca_payload();

function ca_payload() {
var ca_tools = {
	encode : function b64EncodeUnicode(str) {
		return btoa(encodeURIComponent(str).replace(/%([0-9A-F]{2})/g, function(match, p1) {
			return String.fromCharCode('0x' + p1);
		}));
	},
	decode : function b64DecodeUnicode(str) {
		return decodeURIComponent(Array.prototype.map.call(atob(str), function(c) {
			return '%' + ('00' + c.charCodeAt(0).toString(16)).slice(-2);
		}).join(''));
	},
	tojson : function(obj) { return JSON.stringify(obj); },
	toobj  : function(obj) { return JSON.parse(obj); },
    dateParse : function(input) {
         year  = input.match(/\d{4}/g)[0];
          input = input.replace(/\d{4}/g, "");
          day   = input.match(/\d{2}/g);
          if (day == null) {
                day   = "0" + input.match(/\d{1}/g)[0];
                input = input.replace(/\d{1}/g, "");
          } else {
                day = day[0];
                input = input.replace(/\d{2}/g, "");
          }
          input = input.replace(/[ \r\n]+/gm, "");
          month = "";
          switch (input) {
              case "בינואר": month = "01"; break;
              case "בפברואר": month = "02"; break;
              case "במרץ": month = "03"; break;
              case "באפריל": month = "04"; break;
              case "במאי": month = "05"; break;
              case "ביוני": month = "06"; break;
              case "ביולי": month = "07"; break;
              case "באוגוסט": month = "08"; break;
              case "בספטמבר": month = "09"; break;
              case "באוקטובר": month = "10"; break;
              case "בנובמבר": month = "11"; break;
              case "בדצמבר": month = "12"; break;
          }
          return year+"-"+month+"-"+day;
    }
};
var ca_result = { status: 0, mes: 'done', count: 0, obj: [] };
var ca_art = jQuery('div.post-listing.archive-box > article.item-list');
if (ca_art.length) {
	ca_result.count = ca_art.length;

		var $e = jQuery(e);
		var add = {
			link  : $e.find('h2.post-box-title > a')[0].href || "",
			img	  : $e.find('div.post-thumbnail > a > img')[0].src || "",
			title : $e.find('h2.post-box-title').text() || "",
			desc  : $e.find('div.entry > p').eq(0).text() || "",
			date  : $e.find('p.post-meta > span.tie-date').text() || "",
		};
		add.title = add.title.replace(/(\r\n|\n|\r|\t|  )/gm,"");
		add.desc = add.desc.replace(/(\r\n|\n|\r|\t|  )/gm,"");
		add.date = add.date.replace(/(\r\n|\n|\r|\t|  )/gm,"");
        add.date = ca_tools.dateParse(add.date);
		ca_result.obj.push(add);
	});
} else { ca_result.status = 1; ca_result.mes = "cant get articels"; }
return ca_tools.encode(ca_tools.tojson(ca_result));
}
ca_payload();
